summary&timestamp=817.0)\n    2.  [Send all staging links to Jo.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=817.0)\n    3.  [Jo will send links to Madi for review.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=817.0)\n    4.  [Madi will publish the approved pages.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=817.0)\n\n### X-Zek Content\n\n  - [**Status:** 6 articles completed; 4 from last week remain.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=600.0)\n  - [**Action:** Usman will self-publish the full batch of 10 articles.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=617.0)\n      - [**Rationale:** Bypasses Laban's ticket queue, which could cause a 1-day delay.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=617.0)\n  - [**Customer Feedback:** None received.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=648.0)\n\n### Content Strategy: Repetition\n\n  - [**Question:** Is repeating key points across comparison articles acceptable?](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=727.0)\n  - [**Guidance:** Yes, repetition is acceptable because articles serve different discovery paths.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=727.0)\n      - [**Best Practice:** Paraphrase points instead of using exact copy.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=727.0)\n\n### Dashboard Updates\n\n  - [**X-Zek:** Updated on Thursday with articles published during Usman's absence.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-tYdQ?tab=summary&timestamp=662.0)\n  - [**Smith:** Status is unclear. Usman will double-check if the dashboard is current.](https://fathom.video/share/syzRcu9ipUUUXXBCugYzYSv6qdJ-